channel.title: Scripts Needed!
channel.description:
Hey, i need a few COMPLETE working scripts and someone who knows the scripting because if i get an error i want someone to help me fix not just give codes and run off :(,and those scripts would be...
1) Draynor Willow cutter and banker with working anti randoms, anti ban, putting axe back together. 2) Edgeville Yews cutter and banker with working anti randoms, anti ban, putting axe back together. 3) Camelot Flax picker and Spinner and Banker with anti randoms, anti ban. 4) Auto Willow and Yews Fletcher, with anti randoms, anti ban.
If anybody can code these for me that would be a great deal of help :)[br][size=1]Posted at: December 05, 2006, 10:07:44 PM[/size][hr]anybody?

item.title: Scripts Needed!
item.dc:creator: @junior junior
item.description:
@junior wrote:

Hex Key:

What you have asked for is probably beyond generosity. your looking at about 15-20mill of work if it was to be coded from scratch.

Not 15-20m, but nobodys just going to go “oh he requested it and wants it for free so ill just waste my time making that”. There already is a draynor willow chopper out there, Flax picker im not sure about, yew log fletcher I dont think so, and for the edgville yew cutter, the only one I know of was a pay script. The willow chopper can be found in the free scripts section.
